plot: Sofia works to secure her family's strength, while Oz attempts to play both the Falcones and Maronis to his advantage.

After a shipment of Drops gets taken by the Maronis during a transfer, the Falccones' suspect a rat inside their own organization. Oz has to do some quick thinking to throw suspicion on someone else, while attempting to get Sofia to trust him.—Gislef

Oz Cobb deals with the consequences of a failed drug heist and tightens his grip within the Falcone family. Sofia Falcone, recently out of Arkham Asylum, is both cunning and unstable. Despite her distrust of Oz, they form a tenuous alliance as both aim to manipulate the power dynamics within the crime family
